                     <interp inst="t17751206-49-off215" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing two checkshirts, value six shillings, one linen shirt, value three shillings, one pair of men's leather shoes, value four shillings, one silk handkerchief, value three shillings, one pair of cloth breeches, value ten shillings, and one canvas bag. value six pence
            </rs>, the property of 
               
